name: Who Knew? - Enhance The Silence
description: Who knew that we'd all come this far? You knew how this would end from the start.... My first note to you, from the songs and poems i've written about love and life. Enjoy this visual i created using a photograph I've taken and some production of the song I wrote called "Who Knew?" I will be devloping ways for collectors to have access to more music & poetry before anyone else. thanks for you reading this or even listening to some of my music. stay golden -Enhance The Silence
